videos.description: The Trail Blazers come up with a stop and Damian Lillard rockets a pass ahead to Nassir Little for a two-handed finish on the fast break.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lillard finds Little for fast-break dunk) 2021/02/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lillard finds Little for fast-break dunk

videos.description: Nassir Little drives hard to the basket and throws down a dunk all over a contesting Isaiah Roby.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Little flushes dunk on Roby) 2021/02/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Little flushes dunk on Roby

videos.description: Luguentz Dort comes up with the steal and races down the court to flush a dunk on a Trail Blazers defender.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Dort picks the pocket and gets the slam) 2021/02/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dort picks the pocket and gets the slam

videos.description: With Luguentz Dort all in his face, Damian Lillard uses a step-back move to sink a 3-pointer and extend Portland's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lillard drills a 3 in Dort's face) 2021/02/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lillard drills a 3 in Dort's face

videos.description: Despite compiling four early fouls, Damian Lillard comes up clutch in the fourth as he snuffs out the Thunder comeback rally and finishes with 31 points and 10 assists in a Trail Blazers win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Lillard's double-double leads Blazers past Thunder) 2021/02/16 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Lillard's double-double leads Blazers past Thunder

videos.description: The Thunder fight back from 24 points down but are unable to come away with the win vs. the Trail Blazers as Damian Lillard's 31 points are too much to overcome.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Lillard helps Blazers hold off Thunder) 2021/02/16 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Lillard helps Blazers hold off Thunder
